    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "## Ranked targets for `RedundancyLevel` (read-frequency \u00d7 tail-impact)\n\n| Hot path | Call site | Read frequency | Impact |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| Collab ops batch | `collab-ops-feed.ts:138` (`uploadFile act:true`) | Every peer ping + every /bzz fetch on ping-miss | **HIGH** \u2014 on the 10s critical path |\n| Drive share bundle | `lifecycle.ts:169` (`uploadFile act:true`) | Once per accept (cold, urgent) | HIGH \u2014 currently retries with 0-2-5s backoff |\n| Collab manifest snapshot | `collab-manifest-feed.ts:106` | On accept + every member add/revoke | MEDIUM |\n| Drive manifest snapshot | `swarm-client.ts:503` | On recovery + push merges | MEDIUM |\n| Chat history page | `chat-history.ts:215` | On open + pagination | LOW |\n| Public profile feed | `share-manager.ts:29` | Sporadic peer lookups | LOW-MEDIUM \u2014 redundancy helps payload, not feed HEAD |\n\n**Minimal path:** thread `redundancyLevel` through `SwarmClient.uploadFile` / `uploadData` (`swarm-client.ts:212` and `:225-260`), then pass `RedundancyLevel.MEDIUM` at `collab-ops-feed.ts:138` only. Measure before expanding.",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:43.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:43.000Z"
    }
  },
